videos.headline: Mississippi State scores first with pick-six
videos.description: UMass quarterback Ross Comis is picked off by J.T. Gray, who returns it for a 58-yard touchdown to give the Bulldogs an early lead.

videos.headline: Young streaks 66 yards into the red zone
videos.description: Marquis Young finds a gap and bursts down the field on a drive that would lead to a Minutemen field goal.

videos.headline: UMass defense stops Mississippi State
videos.description: On fourth and one, Bulldogs quarterback Nick Fitzgerald attempts a quarterback sneak but is stuffed by the defense. The Minutemen would kick a field goal on the ensuing drive.

videos.headline: UMass' Rodgers jumps route, snags pick-six
videos.description: Bulldogs Nick Fitzgerald's pass is  intercepted by Isaiah Rodgers who returns it 29 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Mississippi State's Fitzgerald passes Manziel for most rush yards in SEC
videos.description: Bulldogs quarterback Nick Fitzgerald runs for 30 yards. He passes Johnny Manziel for fifth-most rushing yards by a quarterback in SEC history.

videos.headline: UMass' Comis goes deep for TD
videos.description: Minutemen quarterback Ross Comis finds a wide open Andy Isabella for a 69-yard touchdown to give UMass a 20-13 lead.

videos.headline: Mississippi State suffers second turnover
videos.description: UMass' Tyler Hayes rips the ball away from wide receiver Jesse Jackson's hands for the interception.

videos.headline: Mississippi State's Mullen: 'We're not playing very hard'
videos.description: Bulldogs head coach Dan Mullen breaks down the mistakes by his team and the improvements that have to come in the second half.

videos.headline: UMass' Whipple: 'Our guys are playing hard'
videos.description: Minutemen head coach Mark Whipple lays out how his team is playing with more confidence this season, but has to keep playing hard.

videos.headline: Mississippi State's Fitzgerald walks into end zone
videos.description: Bulldogs' Nick Fitzgerald finds an opening and rushes 8 yards for a touchdown to tie UMass in the opening minutes of the second half.

videos.headline: Mississippi State's Fitzgerald scores second rushing TD of quarter
videos.description: Bulldogs' Nick Fitzgerald finds a gap and runs into the end zone untouched for his second rushing touchdown of the quarter.

videos.headline: Mississippi State trick play goes awry
videos.description: Bulldogs' wide receiver Reginald Todd lobs it deep to Jesse Jackson but is intercepted by UMass' Isiah Rodgers who returns it 30 yards to midfield.

videos.headline: Mississippi State's Abram ejected on targeting penalty
videos.description: Bulldogs' Jonathan Abram is ejected from the game for a helmet-to-helmet targeting call when he collides with UMass' quarterback Ross Comis.

videos.headline: Mississippi State's Thomas returns punt return 82 yards for TD
videos.description: Bulldogs' Deddrick Thomas returns a UMass punt 87 yards for a touchdown to give Mississippi State a 34-23 lead.

videos.headline: UMass players exchange heated words on the sideline
videos.description: Minutemen teammates Ray Thomas and Jessie Britt push and shove each other in a heated debate on the field.

videos.headline: Mullen proud of UMass win, focused on clash with Bama
videos.description: Mississippi State head coach Dan Mullen is proud of his team and its 34-23 victory over UMass, but is focused on next week's big game against Alabama.

videos.headline: Offense was key to second half for Mississippi State
videos.description: Andre Ware and Taylor Zarzour break down the Bulldogs' victory over an underrated UMass team and their upcoming game against Alabama.

videos.headline: Mississippi State QB Fitzgerald on UMass and second half
videos.description: Bulldogs' Nick Fitzgerald discusses how his mindset changed going into the second half and how he is going to attack next week's challenges against Alabama.

videos.headline: Mississippi State survives UMass' upset bid
videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald does his damage on the ground as he runs in two touchdowns in No. 16 Mississippi State's 34-23 win against UMass.
